ote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n似係 燈係獨立線路支出黎，可能電線/燈具有問題</blockquote><br />\n是咪應該book個技師上黎屋企check？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下搵左邊組燈有問題 再換過盞燈</blockquote><br />\n未必係燈，可能係電器都唔定</blockquote><br />\n佢話一開燈就跳？</blockquote><br />\n係啊<br />\n一開燈就跳全屋fuse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOverload <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇姐過開燈一陣之黎跳<br />\n<br />\n如果無一黎就一開燈跳 就應該燈具有問題<br />\n<br />\n原過搵師傅拎個表黎試試佢最安全</blockquote><br />\n每次都係一開燈就撞fuse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感激巴打意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3098f0dee4212031ec51859ebc6c88fc8eca66ac","tid":183974,"uid":46332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:19:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你買個雜牌差電器?<br />\n<br />\n定原廠?</blockquote><br />\n原廠 一插即爆 火花爆出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊間?</blockquote><br />\nApple 但我想知點解會爆火花</blockquote><br />\n爆電容</blockquote><br />\n電乜撚野容"},{"pid":"a1f807d6dffa5680257230de94901df9a078ab1a","tid":183974,"uid":95437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T19:54:36.000Z","msg":"屌你個掣假到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9030ad55f93bdc5e51870d6686780ccb1c43211","tid":183974,"uid":87517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:16:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n是咪應該book個技師上黎屋企check？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下搵左邊組燈有問題 再換過盞燈</blockquote><br />\n未必係燈，可能係電器都唔定</blockquote><br />\n佢話一開燈就跳？</blockquote><br />\n係啊<br />\n一開燈就跳全屋fuse<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOverload <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇姐過開燈一陣之黎跳<br />\n<br />\n如果無一黎就一開燈跳 就應該燈具有問題<br />\n<br />\n原過搵師傅拎個表黎試試佢最安全</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早幾個月都試過一次 一開燈個燈膽卜一聲仲爆埋火花 全屋跳晒fuse 機房個總制都跳埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26107e4320765cf3af5bafcf5841fd30bf642526","tid":183974,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:21:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順手問埋<br />\n懷疑屋企裝修個陣<br />\n個水電佬將燈線同13a線合埋一條<br />\n有時打緊機<br />\n出面開燈我隻牛就會啪一聲<br />\n<br />\n有時我老母係廳用大火數既電器<br />\n我隻牛就會有 滋滋 聲<br />\n<br />\n宜家可以點解決</blockquote><br />\n轉第二組氣 搵師傅<br />\n不過好q 麻煩<br />\n<br />\n你搵下有冇其他13a so 係另一way<br />\n用果way 黎玩電腦"},{"pid":"6cc33db7bc0517697d0c441799e8cfe623be4bb3","tid":183974,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:27:07.000Z","msg":"隻牛流撚到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真野點會咁小料"},{"pid":"ae7da836311fff204df136013c251aaa0544cefb","tid":183974,"uid":52699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>順手問埋<br />\n懷疑屋企裝修個陣<br />\n個水電佬將燈線同13a線合埋一條<br />\n有時打緊機<br />\n出面開燈我隻牛就會啪一聲<br />\n<br />\n有時我老母係廳用大火數既電器<br />\n我隻牛就會有 滋滋 聲<br />\n<br />\n宜家可以點解決</blockquote><br />\n轉第二組氣 搵師傅<br />\n不過好q 麻煩<br />\n<br />\n你搵下有冇其他13a so 係另一way<br />\n用果way 黎玩電腦</blockquote><br />\n我慘撚過你，20A比冷氣, 13A比S/O 同埋6A 燈線應該放咗一齊 <br />\n<br />\n夏天開住冷氣打機會overload"},{"pid":"06e602de6ca9218f3da7b5992b18e5bed2e6add3","tid":183974,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc